            <input class="char1" type="text" id="you1" value="0"><input class="char1" type="text" id="you2" value="0"><input class="char1" type="text" id="you3" value="0"><input class="char1" type="text" id="you4" value="0">万<input class="char1" type="text" id="you5" value="0"><span class="char6">0</span><span class="char7">0</span><span class="char8">0</span>円
